### useSelect

Hook to access the Select root context. Returns the select state and control functions.

```tsx
import { useSelect } from "heroui-native";

const {
  isOpen,
  onOpenChange,
  isDefaultOpen,
  isDisabled,
  triggerPosition,
  setTriggerPosition,
  contentLayout,
  setContentLayout,
  nativeID,
  closeDelay,
  value,
  onValueChange,
} = useSelect();
```

