> A collapsible content panel for organizing information in a compact space

## Import

```tsx
import { Accordion } from "heroui-native";
```

## Anatomy

```tsx
<Accordion>
  <Accordion.Item>
    <Accordion.Trigger>
      ...
      <Accordion.Indicator>...</Accordion.Indicator>
    </Accordion.Trigger>
