## Hooks

### useAccordion

Hook to access the accordion root context. Must be used within an `Accordion` component.

```tsx
import { useAccordion } from "heroui-native";

const { value, onValueChange, selectionMode, isCollapsible, isDisabled } =
  useAccordion();
```

