| --- | ----- | ----- | --- |
| `id`         | `Key`                         | -           | Unique identifier for the item             |
| `textValue`  | `string`                      | -           | Text value for accessibility and typeahead |
| `isDisabled` | `boolean`                     | `false`     | Whether this item is disabled              |
| `variant`    | `"default" \| "danger"`       | `"default"` | Visual variant                             |
